    "content": {
      "type": "doc",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Qapline was a web ERP system for a logistics company, focused on operational workflows rather than marketing presentation.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "My contribution centered on improving frontend structure by replacing fragmented two-way binding patterns with a more centralized state-management approach using Redux.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "This project shows the type of engineering work I bring to complex internal tools: untangling frontend state, improving predictability, and making the application easier to extend over time.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
